T02D2642:246b-1: a'arya pradzny'a p'a ra mi ta au pa de sha ma n'a ma /
T02D2642:246b-3: 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i
T02D2642:246b-4: man ngag ces bya ba sangs rgyas dang byang chub
T02D2642:246b-5: sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2642:246b-6: sangs rgyas yum gyur de yi ming //
T02D2642:246b-7: rang bzhin med pa'i rang bzhin can //
T02D2642:246b-8: tshig med yul las rnam par 'das //
T02D2642:246b-10: dngos po brgyad sogs rgyas par ni //
T02D2642:246b-11: khong chud nus pa ma yin pas //
T02D2642:246b-12: rjes 'jug spros pa med pa'i don //
T02D2642:246b-13: bdag gis rab tu bshad par bya //
T02D2642:246b-14: snying gi dkyil du gnas pa ni //
T02D2642:246b-15: rdo rje dkar po rnam par mdzes //
T02D2642:246b-16: rtse mo lnga pa gzi brjid can //
T02D2642:246b-17: lte bar thig le dkar po cig / lnga po'i steng du rim bzhin 'bar //
T02D2642:246b-18: pha rol phyin drug rim bzhin dag / rim bzhin thig le sgra spangs la //
T02D2642:246b-19: brtan gyur stobs bskyed ting 'dzin sbyang //
T02D2642:246b-20: man ngag rim pas sgra nang du //
T02D2642:246b-22: 'dab ma stong gi bar du dmigs //
T02D2642:246b-23: slar bsdus sgra yi ngo bo las //
T02D2642:246b-25: de nyid gsal bar bya ba'i phyir //
T02D2642:246b-26: mkhas pa rab tu bsten par gyis //
T02D2642:246b-27: sems can rnams la bdag gsol 'debs //
T02D2642:246b-28: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i man ngag
T02D2642:246b-29: rdo rje lta bu zhes bya ba dpal kampa las
T02D2642:246b-32: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po 'di pam ka ra
T02D2642:246b-33: shr'i dzny'a na'i zhal snga nas bod kyi sgra bsgyur
